description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb discusses the game plan of the Miami Dolphins, the ongoing Ezekiel Elliott situation, NFL GMs, and the difference between the Chargers and the Cowboys. and the debut of Jalen Hurts at Oklahoma.
